longBusinessSummary: HORNBACH Baumarkt AG operates as a do-it-yourself (DIY) retail company in Germany, Austria, the Czech Republic, Luxembourg, the Netherlands, Romania, Slovakia, Sweden, and Switzerland. It operates through Retail and Real Estate segments. The company offers various DIY goods, home improvement goods, and gardening products in hardware/electrical, paint/wallpaper/flooring, construction materials/timber/prefabricated components, sanitary/tiles, and garden divisions. As of February 28, 2021, the company operated 161 DIY megastores with garden centers, 2 specialist stores, and online shops in 9 European countries. The company was founded in 1877 and is based in Bornheim, Germany. HORNBACH Baumarkt AG is a subsidiary of Hornbach Holding AG & Co. KGaA.
